                        "text": "<b>Trigger</b> The moonflower has swallowed a creature; <b>Effect</b> The swallowed creature is wrapped in a tight cocoon and extruded from the moonflower's body into an adjacent square. The creature continues to be Swallowed Whole. It can't use <a aonid=\"1\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Acrobatics</a> to <a aonid=\"79\" game-obj=\"Actions\">Escape</a> a pod, but other creatures can attempt to Rupture the pod. The cocooned creature takes half damage from any damage dealt to the cocoon. Once the cocoon is Ruptured, it deflates and decays.",
